    "The quality re-pass (Refine) uses Whisper. Turbo is the default; the compact variant saves about 1 GB of disk. Choose by selecting a row.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El re-pase de calidad (Refine) usa Whisper. Turbo es el predeterminado; la variante compacta ahorra alrededor de 1 GB de disco. Elige seleccionando una fila."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The refine covers much less speech than the current transcript — it probably failed. Do not apply it.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El refine cubre mucha menos voz que el transcript actual — probablemente falló. No lo apliques."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The rest of the text is preserved as written. Putting the ISO date first makes the library sort meetings automatically.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El resto del texto se conserva tal cual. Poner la fecha ISO primero hace que la biblioteca ordene las reuniones automáticamente."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The transcript does not prove any names — you can rename the pills manually.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El transcript no prueba ningún nombre — puedes renombrar las etiquetas manualmente."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The transcription engine is not available.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El motor de transcripción no está disponible."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Them": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ellos"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "They guide the final summary: they are expanded with facts and marked as yours (▸).": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Guían el resumen final: se expanden con hechos y quedan marcadas como tuyas (▸)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This changes the Portavoz interface only. Meeting transcription and summary languages stay controlled by each meeting.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Esto cambia solo la interfaz de Portavoz. Los idiomas de transcripción y resumen siguen controlados por cada reunión."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This meeting does not keep its audio.": {
